===============================================================================
cross-file-call
===============================================================================
Function in one Python file calls a function defined in another file.
lang: python

--- file: pyproject.toml ---
[project]
name = "sample"

--- file: utils.py ---
def compute(value: int) -> int:
    return value * 2

--- file: app.py ---
from utils import compute

def run() -> int:
    return compute(21)

--- expect:arch-graph ---
